title: Bored ADC LFT
body:
Hi,

im a main adc since season 3. Have played in different teams in ESL over 2 years. Since i finished my bachelor in economics i cant allin on the game that much anymore, but still like the challenge. Apart from working a regular office job im still looking for teams that play in the evening and on the weekend. 
Im incredibly dedicated to the game and really need ppl with the same dedication around me. If you think i fit your team, drop me a message or add me ingame. 

Native German, English is fine too tho.
